data.meta_description: Cisco History - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. 1984 Cisco Facts: Headcount for Fiscal Year: 2 Computer scientists, len bosack and sandy learner, from Stanford university, found Cisco Systems. Bosack and learner's vision is to enable disparate networks to talk with each other and share information reliability. With that idea in mind, the multi-protocol router is born.
